Cashback based loyalty coalition program

18.description:
Koalia is a loyalty coalition program based on cashback which brings together business that want to increase sales and users who want access to interesting promotions. It is 100% digital, free for users and open to anyone who wants to start saving, making it especially attractive for the underbanked.

In a few words, Koalia is an app in which users earn cashback for their purchases in stores that belong to its merchant network. They can also earn other types of rewards based on their loyalty and purchase frequency.

The cashback earned by making use of the promotions can later on be used at any of the stores which belong to the network, expanding access to digital payments for users and merchants.
